  Description: '<color=#FF4444>45 HP</color> | <color=#FFAA00>5 ATK</color> | <color=#00CCFF>45
    EN</color>

    Acts as a protective barrier that analyzes incoming and outgoing
    traffic based on predefined security rules. It blocks unauthorized access attempts
    and malicious data packets, while allowing only trusted connections between your
    network and the outside world.

    It strikes fear into the enemy.

    <color=#BF00FF>Enemies:
    Ransomware, Worm</color>'
